Binani Cement of India Planning to Invest in Mauritius, Le Matinal Reports

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-04-11T05:59:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/binani-cement-to-invest-in-mauritius-le-matinal-says.html
Binani Cement Ltd. (BINC)  of  India  is one
of two new cement companies planning to start operations in
Mauritius, Le Matinal said, without saying where it got the
information.  Holcim (Mauritius) Ltd. and Lafarge (Mauritius) Cement Ltd.
currently produce cement in Mauritius, the Port Louis-based
newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in  Port Louis  at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  